## Pre-requisites

Make sure either you have included `mat-exp-all-styles`, `mat-exp-all-buttons-styles` or `mat-exp-__KEBAB__-styles` in your global SCSS styles.

```scss
@use '@ngm-dev/mat-exp' as mat-exp;

html {
  @include mat-exp.mat-exp-all-styles();
}
```

or

```scss
@use '@ngm-dev/mat-exp' as mat-exp;

html {
  @include mat-exp.mat-exp-all-buttons-styles();
}
```

or

```scss
@use '@ngm-dev/mat-exp' as mat-exp;

html {
  @include mat-exp.mat-exp-__KEBAB__-styles();
}
```

